The 4T dye treated hybrid solar cells fabricated with pristine P3HT and doped P3HT HTMs were next compared with tBP-LiTFSI doped Spiro-OMeTAD HTM. The doped Spiro-OMeTAD and doped P3HT solar cells showed champion efficiencies around 3.31% and 3.95%, respectively (Table 1). This enhanced efficiency in TiO2/4T/doped P3HT/Au device is probably attributed to broader spectral response of TiO2/4T/doped P3HT and the increased hole-mobility of doped P3HT due to the presence of Lithium salt as a dopant. Furthermore, it has been reported that Lithium salt can increase of hole mobility of polymer48,49.Table 1
